  <body>

  <p>
A subtype of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person_property">PERSON PROPERTY</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_cancer_staging">CANCER STAGING</xref>
 describes the severity of a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
's cancer based on the extent of the original (primary) 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_tumour">Tumour</xref>
 and whether or not cancer has spread in the body.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_cancer_staging">CANCER STAGINGS</xref>
, see the 
    <xref href="https://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/factsheet/Detection/staging"
            scope="external"
            format="html">National Cancer Institute website</xref>
.  </p>

